<dl id="n40035f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40035f">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40035f"> 35(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> schoolgoing age</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&ldquo;I know that we have about 800 Christian children of school-going age in the Mission and that 500 at least are out of reach of education of even the most elementary description. I know that, if they are not taught to read, the Bible will be a closed book to them, and that, if they have no schooling, they will in all probability grow up to a life scarcely distinguishable from slavery. Yet there is no teacher to send.&rdquo; <small> Rev W.S. Hunt, <a name="WSHI1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WSHI1"><cite title="source">India's Outcastes: A New Era</cite></a> (1924) 73</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
